# Marketing Campaign Response Prediction

## Goal
Predict whether a customer will subscribe to a term deposit and identify the most important drivers to improve targeting.

## Tools
Python (pandas, scikit-learn), Kaggle  
Optional: Power BI

## Deliverables
- Kaggle notebook (reproducible workflow)
- Insights summary (key drivers + recommendations)
- Optional dashboard (Power BI)

## Links
- Kaggle dataset: https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/janiobachmann/bank-marketing-dataset
